      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content</head>
<p>The collection consists of photocopies of ca. 159 letters from four Hemingway correspondents whose papers are in the University of Virginia Library: John Dos Passos, Katharine F. Smith Dos Passos, William Faulkner, and A.E. Hotchner.</p>
         <p>Letters by William Faulkner in this collection are
         listed below.</p>
      </scopecontent>
